<screenshot>
<mediaobject>
<imageobject>
<imagedata fileref="instab1.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject>
</mediaobject>
</screenshot>

<para
>Le bhokisi yencoko yababini yahlulwe kumacala amabini.</para>

<para
>Icala lasekunene lebhokisi yencoko yababini ikunikeza isalathiso esikhawulezayo esibonwayo kubungakanani bemiqolo nemihlathi ezakwenziwa kwindlela yemigca. Oku kuluncedo kwi <quote
>iyabala</quote
> ngaphandle kwendlela yakho yemigca. Awunakuhlela ubeko lwendlela yakho yemigca apha.</para>

<para
>Icala lasekhohlo lebhokisi yencoko yababini liqulathe iibhokisi ezimbini zolahlo phantsi, kwaye iibhokisi zokhetho ezinamanani amabini.</para>

<para
>Ibhokisi yokhetho yenani enombhalo <guilabel
>Inani leMiqolo</guilabel
>, ikuvumela ukhankanye ukusuka ku 1 ukuya ku 128 imiqolo kwindlela yemigca.</para>

<para
>Ibhokisi yokhetho yenani enombhalo <guilabel
>Inani leMihlathi</guilabel
>, ikuvumela ukhankanye ukusuka ku 1 ukuya ku 128 imihlathi kwindlela yemigca.</para>

<para
>Ngexesha unyenyisa noba yenye yezi nketho, ibhokisi yemboniso inyenyisa kwizicwangciso ezintsha zakho.</para>

<para
>Ibhokisi yolahlo phantsi enombhalo <guilabel
>Ubude beSeli</guilabel
>, ingacwangciswa noba kwiinketho ezimbini.</para>

<variablelist
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Ngokuzenzekela</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Ukuba olu khetho lukhethiwe, &kword; izakucwangcisa ubude beseli yeseli nganyhe kwindlela yemigca entsha ukuya kubungakanani obusekwe kubungakanani bokubhaliweyo kwangoku. &kword; ayizukunikeza ngokuzenzekelayo isithuba esongezelelweyo kwiseli nganye, kuba uzoba indlela yemigca enkulu (okanye encinane) kunokufunekayo.</para
> <para
>Njengomzekelo, ukub awenza indlela yemigca kwimiqolo emithathu, akukhathaliseki ukuba u <quote
>zoba</quote
> indlela yemigca njenge 1 intshi ubude, okanye 4 ii intshi ubude, ubude beseli nganye buzakusekwa kubungakanani bokubhaliweyo bangoku.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Incwadi yesandla</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Xa iklhethiwe, bala ubude beseli ngokwahlula ubungakanani bomsebenzisi bendlela yemigca ngenani lemiqolo.</para
> <para
>Ukuba oku kukhethiwe, kwaye wenza indlela yemigca kwimiqolo emithathu ne <quote
>zoba</quote
> indlela yemigca  3 ii intshi ubude, iseli nganye izakuba yi 1 intshi kubude. Ukuba uzoba indlela yemigca 1.5 ii intshi ubude, iseli nganye izakuba yi 0.5 ii intshi ubude. </para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> </variablelist>

<para
>Ibhokisi yolahlo phantsi enombhalo <guilabel
>Ububanzi beseli</guilabel
>, inga cwangciswa noba kukwinketho ezimbini.</para>

<variablelist
> <varlistentry
> <term
