></keycombo
></para
> </listitem
> <listitem
> <para
>okanye ngokunqakraza <inlinemediaobject
><imageobject
><imagedata fileref="framemode.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject
></inlinemediaobject
> kwibar-yesixhobo.</para
> </listitem
> </itemizedlist
> </step
> <step
> <para
>Ngoku khetha enye yezimbini (okanye ngaphezulu) iiseli ofuna ukuzidibanisa kwenye. Ungakwenza oku ngokunqakraza kanye kwiseli nge <mousebutton
