> <para
>Ngoku bamba phantsi i &Shift; isitshixo kwaye nqakraza kwiseli kwesinye isiphelo somqolo okanye umhlathi ofuna ukuwudibanisa.</para
> <para
>Zonke iiseli phakathi kwezi seli zimbini zizakukhethwa.</para
