<imageobject>
<imagedata fileref="savetmpl4.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject>
</mediaobject>
</screenshot>

<para
>This is an example of a new category named
<guilabel
>Newsletters</guilabel
>, with a new template named
<guilabel
>Monthly</guilabel
>.</para>

